                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="keyword">shimmerColor</span> has no effect unless
                    <span class="keyword">variant="shimmer"</span>.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Border and fill visuals assume sufficient <span
                        class="keyword"
                        >text/background
                    </span> contrast from consumer styling.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Unknown variant values are typed against in TS, but fallback
                    class resolution becomes empty at runtime.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div> -->

        <!-- COMPONENTS API SECTION -->
        <div class="docs-intro-section" id="components-api">
            <h2 class="docs-subtitle">Components API</h2>
            <ul class="docs-list">
                <li>
